                        <interp inst="t18460511-name-1129" type="given" value="GEORGE JOHN"></interp>GEORGE JOHN PAYNTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with Mr. Neal. I brought the shin of beef on the 2nd of April—it came to 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—the prisoner came down and asked me if 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. would not do—I said I could not take any less than 35.6i., at I gave 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for it—he went up, and came down again and said, "Very well, Mrs. Kent will call and pay"—he did not give me any money.</p>
